===== > Application object =====

The following objects are directly related to the ''application'' API.

==== Application ====

The application object has the following properties.

^  Property  ^  Type  ^  Description  ^
| applicationid  | string  | //(readonly)// ID of the application.  |
| **hostid** \\ (required) | string | ID of the host that the application belongs to. \\ \\ Cannot be updated. |
| **name** \\ (required) | string | Name of the application |
| flags | integer | //(readonly)// Origin of the application. \\ \\ Possible values: \\ 0 - a plain application; \\ 4 - a discovered application.  |
| templateids | array | //(readonly)// IDs of the parent template applications. |